snippet: Michelle Wie shot a six-under-par 66 for a share of the first-round lead with Angela Stanford and Candie Kung in the Lorena Ochoa Invitational in Guadalajara, Mexico.
abstract: Michelle Wie, Angela Stanford and Candie Kung share first-round lead at LPGA's Lorena Ochoa Invitational golf tournament in Guadalajara, Mexico; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Michelle Wie shot a six-under-par 66 for a share of the first-round lead with Angela Stanford and Candie Kung in the Lorena Ochoa Invitational in Guadalajara, Mexico.

headline.main: Wie Is in Three-Way Tie for Lead
